{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681570/extras/entervagrientdiscordbanner.gif?t=1738181934\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Vagrient, an Armlys alien separated from his clan at war in another solar system. A corrupted warpgate stands between, placing a halt to his return. Power must be restored to the gate! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SOLO DEVELOPED  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover and use warpgates to travel from one planet to another</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a vast solar system of planets potentially containing what Vagrient desires</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in combat with other entities whilst managing energy output and consumption</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight unique bosses, learn and strategize against there moves </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tackle any puzzles and obstacles that get in the way of the main objective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn new skills, allowing for different movement and combat techniques </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plus lots of other exciting content to uncover and experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681570/extras/orb_gif.gif?t=1738181934\" />Find and consume a variety of these energy orbs, each having a different use case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681570/extras/unstableenergyboltgif.gif?t=1738181934\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738181934","backg